#scope of the project
The primary objective of this project is to analyze credit card customer data using SQL for data preparation and Power BI for data visualization. This project aims to extract meaningful insights
into customer demographics, credit usage behavior, and financial patterns to support data-driven decision-making for customer management and risk assessment.

