1.	Data Cleaning & Transformation:
o	Handle missing or invalid values.
o	Normalize and join datasets.
o	Create new derived metrics like credit utilization (Balance / Credit_Limit), payment ratio (Payments / Purchases), etc.
2.	Analytical Queries:
o	Total customers by gender, location, age group.
o	Average credit usage by demographic.
o	Identify high-risk customers (e.g., high utilization + low payment).
o	Segment customers based on usage patterns.
